ygData.messageBody:
I've seen some bad one on E'ci but none as bad as the previously mentioned
Balonie Sandwych. I know for a fact she was reported at least a half dozen
times by guild members of mine. One of them quit the game after the
response from a GM who basically told him to shut up and mind his own
business, though not that nicely. She must know somebody. Some were clever
puns, mostly gnomes, but others???

How about:

Mulee Packanimal Who takes a mule to 20th level?
Supermodel Name eventually changed
Halfdead Elfzman
Halfelf How the heck did this get thru?

My favorite pun though has to be the monk named Thelonius

Kitasi
